These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  firefighter, librarian
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, train
1. the librarian is on the left or right of the firefighter##3
2. the person driving the train is on the right of the librarian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| Job   | librarian  | firefighter |
| Transport       | airplane | train |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: disco, reggae
There are 2 different nationalities: german, argentine
1. the argentine is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
2. the fan of reggae is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| Music-Genre   | disco | reggae |
| Nationality      | argentine     | german  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-3::.
2 different pets are kept: snake, frog
The people use 2 different means of transport: car, ship
1. the person driving the car is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
2. the person driving the car is on the left or right of the owner of the frog##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Pet   | snake | frog  |
| Transport   | car | ship |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-4::.
