The people use 2 different means of transport: train, ship
1. the person driving the train is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
2. the person playing poker is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |
| Game   | snooker | poker   |
| Transport       | ship | train |

